This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for sentence embeddings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of sparse representations and evaluation metrics, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper applies its techniques to movie dialogs and scene descriptions, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
